➜传祺没有弯道？全副武装到牙齿，GA8、GM8、GS8齐亮相！
http://www.sohu.com/a/416890354_99994080	29806
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200907/6faf544e6558402da0d3512eb7fae017.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
